	   <tr><td colspan=2>The Dwarf is by far the best race.&nbsp;&nbsp;You winder why everyone plays a Dwarf Cleric, it's cause they are the best.<br><br>Haflings are great, if not Dwarves be haflings.  Short people are the best.<br><br>High Elves are stuck up.  They think since they have the higher starting wisdom that it makes up for their 60 str and low stam, don't be fooled.<br><br>DE's are just cool for roleplaying purposes and Gnomes are....well their a challenge I suppose.<br><br>Eberk Ghalea<br>22 Dwf Cleric<br>Mithaniel Marr<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
